      <section eId="sec_2152">
        <num>2152</num>
        <heading>Typhoid fever; carriers; care and maintenance, payment of expenses</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_2152__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>A verified statement of any such approved expense incurred\npursuant to this section and sections two thousand one hundred fifty and\ntwo thousand one hundred fifty-one of this chapter, shall be transmitted\nto the commissioner.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_2152__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>The commissioner shall examine the statement and if satisfied that\nsuch authorized expenses are correct and necessary in accordance with\nrules and regulations adopted by him he shall audit and allow the same\nand when so audited the amount thereof shall be paid by the state\ndepartment of taxation and finance, on the warrant of the state\ncomptroller to the institution, agency or person.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
